{"tid":602544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推大型垃圾桶搭港鐵　老翁涉偷垃圾桶被捕","createTime":"2018-03-23T05:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T11:30:01.000Z","uid":20933,"like":102,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"50423fbc1d8ac1712b90e04213fbe8cc5d3f3c9d","tid":602544,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180323/large/1521780990_07b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F1521780990_07b1.jpg&h=44a710b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕一名老翁，他涉嫌偷垃圾桶被捕。警方稱，今晨10時許，街坊報案指有人在黃大仙下邨龍豐樓的樓層偷垃圾桶。警員到場調查後，拘捕一名年約80歲的老翁。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯的外貌與昨日網上瘋傳、堆垃圾桶搭港鐵的老翁非常相似。該圖片顯示，一名滿頭白髮的老翁，推着有污迹的綠色大型垃圾桶乘搭港鐵。身旁乘客都掩着鼻子，更有人急急走開。老翁由黃大仙站搭到石硤尾站，最終被職員勸退，推着垃圾桶離開。<br />\n<br />\n據報當時為中午12時，車廂內也相當多乘笿；該個垃圾桶為綠色揭蓋式，就是屋邨常用的一種。<br />\n<br />\n有網民質疑：「點解咁大個垃圾桶都可搭車？&hellip;&hellip;點樣入閘㗎？職員咁都睇唔到？」<br />\n<br />\n每名乘搭巿區線列車乘客，只可攜帶一件長闊高相加後不得超過1.7米，而任何一邊長度不可超過1.3米行李或物品，否則職員有權拒絕其乘車。根據港鐵附例第27A條，任何人攜帶對使用鐵路其他人造成滋擾或不便的行李、物品或其他東西進入鐵路處所，均屬違例，最高可判罰2千元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180323/large/1521783039_1670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F1521783039_1670.jpg&h=949cd301&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec2bc907196167f6f1059d643651811403a84702","tid":602544,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57984451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57984451&d=0ukGSjiNL14Cx8Un7%2B1nc57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d69ffa3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57984451&h=31701631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57984451</a>"},{"pid":"b175553d8747c882e112a5c61ef582f02afb310d","tid":602544,"uid":30081,"like":151,"dislike":1,"score":150,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:39:03.000Z","msg":"阿伯無錢買棺材姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db56d1334c4dd73c05e7a752d65e3fa05d5034d2","tid":602544,"uid":169116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾筒有乜好偷呢?"},{"pid":"52c7a30c3aa0959cfcdb295eed3e62936842a6ff","tid":602544,"uid":109557,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"港鐵唔罰佢錢？  咁大個行李"},{"pid":"728885f3e99d917c88183993d04291ebb21c46eb","tid":602544,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:42:02.000Z","msg":":<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051264b9427c9038acad376f0594531281875caf","tid":602544,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":84,"score":-80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f53fba5137b558067a4b37228fdac0489daaf33","tid":602544,"uid":107639,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"無錢想食皇家飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e9e181701aae7f4b1260cec0c89b0a2291f5df","tid":602544,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"db56d1334c4dd73c05e7a752d65e3fa05d5034d2","tid":602544,"uid":169116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾筒有乜好偷呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"訓"},{"pid":"d4315ef416f8697fa31775d62ee4b73cf22ad56c","tid":602544,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />